  "keyFeatures": [
    "Automatic URLSession network request capture via URLSessionProxy or PulseProxy",
    "Persistent log storage using CoreData with efficient lzfse compression",
    "Built-in SwiftUI console (ConsoleView) for on-device log inspection",
    "Real-time remote logging to Pulse Pro macOS/iOS app over local network",
    "Sensitive data redaction for headers, query items, and JSON fields",
    "Response mocking for debugging via MockingURLProtocol",
    "SwiftLog backend integration via PulseLogHandler",
    "Session-based log organization with export to .pulse format"
  ],
